    <h1 style="max-width:none;margin-bottom:12px;">tools &amp; guides for <em class="glow-text">smarter renewals.</em></h1>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--pencil);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 0;line-height:1.6;">everything we publish to help you track, understand, and reduce your auto-renewal exposure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="lp-section" style="padding-top:0;">
  <div class="wrap">

    <div class="resources-grid">

      <a href="/tool" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">🧮</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">tool</div>
        <h3>cost explorer</h3>
        <p>select your providers across insurance, broadband, subscriptions, domains, and business services. see your estimated annual overpayment based on uk loyalty penalty averages.</p>
        <span class="resource-cta">open calculator →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/comparison" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">⚖️</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">tool</div>
        <h3>set-it-and-forget-it comparison</h3>
        <p>side-by-side comparison of how perch. stacks up against doing nothing, using a spreadsheet, or paying a personal finance app. 16 criteria.</p>
        <span class="resource-cta">see comparison →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/demo" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">🖥️</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">demo</div>
        <h3>interactive product demo</h3>
        <p>watch perch. parse renewal emails in real-time. see the full flow from forward to verdict to digest — right in your browser. no sign-up needed.</p>
        <span class="resource-cta">try the demo →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">📝</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">blog</div>
