        <p>in-depth articles on the loyalty penalty, auto-renewal traps, subscription waste, and how the uk market is structured to benefit from your inattention.</p>
        <span class="resource-cta">read the blog →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/proof" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">data</div>
