        <span class="resource-cta">view the data →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/features" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">reference</div>
        <h3>full feature catalogue</h3>
        <p>every capability perch. offers, from email parsing to vendor benchmarking. understand exactly what each tier includes and what it costs.</p>
        <span class="resource-cta">browse features →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/how-it-works" class="resource-card">
        <div class="resource-icon">🔧</div>
        <div class="resource-tag">guide</div>
        <h3>how perch. works</h3>
